<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/stylesheets/home.css"/>

<h1>Incriminate</h1>
	<p id="first">
		Incriminate was designed with the sole purpose of playing practical jokes on your friends.  Simply fill out the forms with a person's name and age, and this application will handle the rest.  Incriminate will generate a ficticious police report with the information you provide.  You can even send the report to anyone you want!
	</p>

<br>

<h2>Add a new target:</h2>

<form method="POST" action="/search">
	<p>
		<label class="nameagemail" for="search">Name:</label>
		<input type="text" required name="name" id = "search" placeholder="name...." autofocus>
	</p>
	<p>
		<label class="nameagemail" for="age">Age:&nbsp</label>
		<input type="text" name="age" id = "age" placeholder="age...." autofocus>
	</p>
	<p>
		<label class="nameagemail" for="email">Send Arrest Report to:</label>
		<input type="email" required name="email" id = "email" placeholder="email...." autofocus>
	</p>
	<p>
	<input type="hidden" name="UserId" value ="<%= user.id %>">
	<input type="submit" class ="btn btn-default btn-lg" value ="Incriminate here!">
	</p>
</form>

<br>

